definitions.definition: A crustacean larva that has three pairs of locomotive organs (corresponding to antennules , antennae , and mandibles ), a median eye , and little or no segmentation of the body .

main_definition: ( zoology ) A crustacean larva that has three pairs of locomotive organs (corresponding to antennules , antennae , and mandibles ), a median eye , and little or no segmentation of the body . [from mid 19th c.]
